# Local Data Cache Execution
# We ignore the massive raw scrape dumps, but explicitly DO NOT ignore the `processed` dir
# because the GitHub Actions runner needs to commit insights.json back to the repo 
# daily to preserve the AI's 'Temporal Memory' across ephemeral runs.
data/raw/
